latestIgtvVideos.title: Hey guys.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hope you are safe and at home:)
So many of you face problem of more visibility of fine lines and wrinkles under the eye area after applying the foundation so here i m with simple trick /hack which can help u to achieve a flawless look with minimise appearance of lines...so guys do watch and try and let me know in the comment sections. 
Steps are- 
1. Start with colour corrector.
2. Don’t blend it yet.
3. Add concealor on top .
4. Dampen beauty blendor.
5. Add long lasting setting spray.
6. Wait 30 Sec.
7. Now blend it.
8. Then slightly add your favourite setting powder.
9. Add setting spray.
10. Less crease and long lasting makeup.
